enhancementLevel.high:
Create a premium, cinematic-quality illustration suitable for book covers, merchandise, or portfolio presentation. Maximum detail, professional lighting, sophisticated rendering without heavy outlines. Generate an image in 8K resolution with the same aspect ratio as the reference image.

Task: Create a premium, award-quality character illustration inspired by this sketch.

Reference Image: {uploaded_child_drawing}

Core Requirements:
1. SINGLE CHARACTER FOCUS: Render ONLY the main character from the reference drawing. DO NOT include other animals, characters, people, creatures, or companions. NO secondary or background characters, creatures, or supporting elements under any circumstances. Absolute single-subject composition.
2. PRESERVE CORE IDENTITY: Maintain all distinctive features, facial characteristics, markings, personality traits, and visual identity from the original sketch. Character must be instantly recognizable as derived from the original.
3. COLOR FIDELITY: Preserve the original color palette as the foundation. Enhance with rich saturation, depth, and subtle color variation while maintaining the core colors.
4. STYLE MASTERY (CRITICAL - NO HEAVY OUTLINES):
   - For 3D: Render with cinematic lighting (key light, fill light, rim light), ray-traced shadows, physically accurate materials (skin, fabric, wood, metal, fur). Rich surface detail and texture. Soft, natural edge definition through lighting and material properties only. NO black outlines or cell-shading effects.
   - For cartoon: Advanced rendering with sophisticated color gradients, texture overlays, and VARIABLE LINE WEIGHT (thinner, softer lines in shadow areas; crisper, more defined lines for primary silhouettes and focal points). NOT uniform heavy black outlines. Expressive details with refined line work.
   - For anime: High-fidelity cel-shading with SOPHISTICATED EDGE RENDERING - soft, subtle outlines in shadow areas and recessed edges; crisp, defined lines only for primary character silhouettes and dramatic contours. NOT heavy, uniform black borders. Detailed clothing, dynamic hair with strand definition, and subtle facial expressions.
5. COMPOSITION: Dynamic, engaging pose that conveys personality and energy. Full-body or full-subject representation.
6. ENVIRONMENTAL CONTEXT: Subtle atmospheric depth and grounding plane only. For 3D: soft, blurred environmental lighting that doesn't distract from character. For cartoon/anime: minimal background elements (soft color gradients, simple atmospheric effects, or light suggestions of setting) that enhance without competing. Environment should use depth of field or blur to keep character in sharp focus.
7. TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS: 8K resolution (7680 x 4320 or equivalent). Professional color grading. Museum or portfolio-quality output. Sophisticated rendering without artificial outlines.
8. DETAIL MASTERY: Every element refined - hair texture and individual strands, fabric weaves and material authenticity, facial micro-expressions and emotional depth, material properties realistic and compelling. Premium finish throughout.

Character Details:
- Name: {character_name}
- Type: {character_type}
- Age Group Target: {target_age_group}
- Original Colors: {original_colors}
- Distinctive Features: {distinctive_features}
- Special Ability/Trait: {special_ability}

Deliverables: 8K resolution, premium book cover or portfolio-grade quality, merchandise-ready professional illustration, single character focus only, sophisticated rendering without heavy outlines or cell-shading artifacts.

